						<div class="entry-meta">
				<span class="sep">Posted on </span><a href="https://asiansecurityblog.wordpress.com/2014/10/27/my-h-net-book-review-of-acharyas-the-end-of-the-american-world-order/" title="5:45 pm" rel="bookmark"><time class="entry-date" datetime="2014-10-27T17:45:02+09:00">October 27, 2014</time></a><span class="by-author"> <span class="sep"> by </span> <span class="author vcard"><a class="url fn n" href="https://asiansecurityblog.wordpress.com/author/asiansecurityblog/" title="View all posts by Robert E Kelly" rel="author">Robert E Kelly</a></span></span>			</div><!-- .entry-meta -->
			
